snippet.title: Bunny Reversi - Xbox One Gameplay
snippet.description:
Classic Reversi game, also known as Othello, now comes to fully 3D!

Play with one of the 4 characters to develop logical and strategic thinking, to anticipate the moves of your opponent and evaluate your moves and their consequences.

Kick chickens to have a fun! Kick your oponent if they bothers you!

Explore cute little environment.

Bunny Reversi, Bunny Casual series (C) DillyFrame
Also released on Steam, Nintendo Switch and PlayStation 4.

NOTE: Achievements and trophies are only available on Steam and PS4 versions, as the Xbox One version was released via Xbox Creators Program.
